subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
Coaches and Managers
lead_paragraph: A center on North Carolina’s women’s basketball team transferred to Harvard to learn from the only coach to lead a No. 16 team to victory in an N.C.A.A. tournament game.
